See the INSTALL file for an explanation of the compilation and installation procedure.  

EXTERNAL LIBRARIES 

Binaries and headers of the following libraries are required:  

gtkmm-2.4 >= 2.12 
gtkglextmm-1.2
cairomm-1.0 
gl 
glu
boost >= 1.42

COMPILER

The code uses many features of the upcoming C++ standard (C++0x) which have to be supported by the compiler.
To ensure proper compilation, gcc >= 4.5 is recommended as the default compiler.
    